title: SYNIOT Security Smart Lock Deadbolt, Fingerprint Scanner, Keyless Entry Door Lock with Fingerprint or Password or IC card, App Unlock and Control, Touchscreen Keypad
desc: Syniot smart lock SISL-G012 is a tilted-structure design with an appearance patent.
